title: GET_FIRST_BLIP_INFO_ID
content:
0x1BEDE233E6CD2A1F0x64C0273D// GetFirstBlipInfoId
Blip GET_FIRST_BLIP_INFO_ID(int blipSprite);Parameters:blipSprite: Sprite ID, see the Blips Game Reference for the full list.Returns: Returns the first blip ID in an interator that has the specified blip sprite.Also see GET_NEXT_BLIP_INFO_ID for an example.
